OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTeaching union calls for   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FOfsted to be abolished     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Teaching union NASUWT has approved a   
OL,6, motion calling for the abolition of    
OL,7, Ofsted, adding to growing pressure on  
OL,8, the schools watchdog.                  
OL,10,FTeachers described a "deep-seated fear"
OL,11,Fof Ofsted inspections at the union's   
OL,12,Fannual conference in Glasgow on Monday.
OL,14,FLast month, the National Education     
OL,15,FUnion also called for an immediate     
OL,16,Ffreeze to inspections.                 
OL,18,FOfsted has said most school leaders    
OL,19,Ffind inspections "constructive and     
OL,20,Fcollaborative".                        
